content.rendered:
Reading Time: < 1 minute

Jenna Dewan couldn’t be more excited to be engaged.

Then again, have you seen her fiance? We’re shocked this actress took her mouth off Channing Tatum long enough to share such feelings.

“I’m just so freaking happy,” Dewan said to People Magazine. “It’s great.”

Jenna Dewan is engaged to Channing Tatum. We’d say each side made out well in this arrangement.

As for the actual wedding, Dewan says she and Tatum aren’t in a rush to pick up a band or flowers just yet.

“I need to enjoy being engaged. With our schedules, it’s so hard.”
